@startuml Deployment and Resume State Diagram
!theme plain
title Deployment & Resume State Machine\nAI Feature Pipeline - Section 2.1

' State definitions
state "IDLE" as idle : No deployment in progress
state "LOADING_CONTEXT" as loading : Loading PR metadata\nLoading branch protection report\nLoading deployment config
state "ASSESSING_READINESS" as assessing : Fetching fresh PR data\nValidating status checks\nValidating reviews\nChecking branch staleness
state "READY" as ready : All requirements met\nNo blockers detected
state "BLOCKED" as blocked : Deployment blocked\nBlockers recorded
state "SELECTING_STRATEGY" as selecting : Evaluating config\nChecking feature flags\nDetermining merge method
state "AUTO_MERGING" as auto_merging : Enabling GitHub auto-merge\nWaiting for GitHub to merge
state "MANUAL_MERGING" as manual_merging : Directly merging PR\nvia GitHub API
state "DISPATCHING_WORKFLOW" as dispatching : Triggering GitHub Actions\nworkflow dispatch
state "MERGED" as merged : PR successfully merged\nMerge SHA recorded
state "WORKFLOW_TRIGGERED" as workflow_triggered : Workflow dispatch successful\nDeployment handed off to Actions
state "FAILED" as failed : Deployment failed\nError recorded
state "PERSISTING" as persisting : Writing deployment.json\nRecording audit trail

' Initial state
[*] --> idle

' Normal flow
idle --> loading : triggerDeployment()
loading --> assessing : [context loaded]
loading --> failed : [missing pr.json]

assessing --> ready : [eligible = true\nblockers = 0]
assessing --> blocked : [eligible = false\nblockers > 0]
assessing --> failed : [GitHub API error]

ready --> selecting : [proceed]
blocked --> persisting : [record blockers]

' Strategy selection
selecting --> auto_merging : [strategy = AUTO_MERGE\nauto-merge enabled\nallowed by protection]
selecting --> manual_merging : [strategy = MANUAL_MERGE\nauto-merge disabled OR\nnot allowed]
selecting --> dispatching : [strategy = WORKFLOW_DISPATCH\nworkflow configured]

' Execution paths
auto_merging --> merged : [auto-merge enabled\nGitHub merges PR]
auto_merging --> failed : [enableAutoMerge() error\nnode_id missing]

manual_merging --> merged : [mergePullRequest() success\nSHA returned]
manual_merging --> failed : [merge conflict\nrate limit\nAPI error]

dispatching --> workflow_triggered : [triggerWorkflow() success\ndispatch accepted]
dispatching --> failed : [workflow not found\ninvalid inputs\nAPI error]

' Persistence and completion
merged --> persisting : [record merge SHA]
workflow_triggered --> persisting : [record workflow URL]
failed --> persisting : [record error]

persisting --> [*] : [outcome persisted\ndeployment.json updated]

' Resume paths (blocked → ready)
blocked --> idle : [resume: operator resolves blockers]
note right of blocked
  **Resume Scenarios:**
  - Operator requests approvals
  - CI fixes failing checks
  - Branch rebased to be up-to-date
  - Conflicts resolved
  Then re-run: ai-feature deploy
end note

' Guard conditions
note right of assessing
  **Readiness Checks:**
  1. PR state = open (not closed)
  2. PR not draft
  3. No merge conflicts (mergeable = true)
  4. Required status checks passing
  5. Sufficient approving reviews
  6. Branch up-to-date (if strict mode)
end note

note right of selecting
  **Strategy Decision Tree:**
  1. Blockers exist → BLOCKED
  2. Workflow inputs → WORKFLOW_DISPATCH
  3. prevent_auto_merge = true → MANUAL_MERGE
  4. enable_auto_merge = false → MANUAL_MERGE
  5. Protection disallows auto-merge → MANUAL_MERGE
  6. Otherwise → AUTO_MERGE
end note

note left of blocked
  **Blocker Types:**
  - status_checks: Required checks failing
  - reviews: Insufficient approvals
  - branch_stale: Branch behind base
  - conflicts: Merge conflicts
  - draft: PR in draft mode
  - closed: PR not open
  - protection: Branch protection violation
  - approvals: Deploy gate or other approvals pending
end note

note left of merged
  **Success Metadata:**
  - merge_sha: Commit SHA from merge
  - timestamp: ISO 8601
  - strategy: Which path was taken
  - approvals_hash: Audit reference
  - protection_report_hash: Compliance ref
end note

' Options and overrides
note bottom of idle
  **Deployment Options:**
  - --dry-run: Assess without executing
  - --force: Override blockers (admin)
  - --merge-method: Specify merge/squash/rebase
  - --workflow-inputs: Custom workflow params
end note

' Error handling
note bottom of failed
  **Error Recovery:**
  - Rate limit → Retry with backoff
  - Transient error → Retry
  - Human action required → Exit with code 30
  - Permanent error → Exit with code 1
  All errors recorded in deployment.json
end note

@enduml
